channel.title: Client freezes in bank?
channel.description: So on my old computer (32bit) i could sscroll endlessly in my bank without any problems. now for some reason on my current computer (64bit) it freezes when i get about 10-12 lines down. i think it's the models that are installed to the client. but idk. i cant really check without it freezing. The weirdest thing is i didn't change anything but the jdk version when i changed computers. this actually is the client i took from the old one (literally stole it off the hard drive)
